<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="GameHelp India privacy policy for the on-device complaint draft tool and website requests." canonicalPath="/privacy/">
<main id="main"><article class="prose"><span class="kicker">Privacy first</span><h1>Privacy policy</h1><p>GameHelp India does not require an account and does not ask users to upload financial documents.</p><h2>Complaint draft tool</h2><p>The complaint tool generates text inside your browser. The form has no submission endpoint and the entered values are not intentionally transmitted to GameHelp India.</p><h2>Hosting logs</h2><p>Our hosting provider may process standard request information such as IP address, user agent and requested URL for delivery, security and abuse prevention.</p><h2>Analytics and advertising</h2><p>The starter site does not include analytics or advertising trackers. This policy must be updated before either is added.</p><h2>Sensitive information</h2><p>Do not enter or send OTPs, UPI PINs, passwords, full identity documents, card PINs or CVV through this website or any community account.</p></article></main>
</BaseLayout>
